{"tid":1877464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"夏寶龍係乜料，大家睇清楚先","createTime":"2020-02-13T04:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T15:30:43.000Z","uid":92188,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"04ed4446c29eb6bc529f6382010751ef40179e35","tid":1877464,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"[#突發] 每次公司要燉冬菇，都會抽空佢duties，assign分管日常工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外溫馨提示，明報資訊：<br />\n<br />\n//夏寶龍1952年12月出生，早年在天津官至常務副市長，2003年底與寧波書記黃興國對調，到浙江擔任省委副書記，後再升浙江省長，十八大後接替趙洪祝出任省委書記。<br />\n<br />\n他在2013年起力推「三改一拆」，即整改舊住宅區、舊廠區、城中村改造和拆除違法建築，其間摧毀逾2000間基督教堂的十字架以至整座建築物，又引發多宗流血衝突。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3040996749267788/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F3040996749267788%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=672f3fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3040996749267788/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0749cb724441c3ec21a3a6b9168b596c57981837","tid":1877464,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/new3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2Fnew3.jpg&h=88aa5e7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"033325baf9c5c133b2c535ec007011717f8d296a","tid":1877464,"uid":289733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"換另一個死仆街出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天滅中共</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5aefed10f3ce37fdd5c8d95077b61e489d755e80","tid":1877464,"uid":110313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"只係換個更強勢既人出黎<br />\n講到清算咁樣樣<br />\n當年強拆單野都話夏寶龍人清算啦<br />\n當風頭過咗咪又返黎<br />\n清算喎<br />\n我要係支亡呀<br />\n唔係清算呀"},{"pid":"a8